 4. the gothic-revival house is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the wooden house is between the ranch-style house and the photographer##2
 6. the modern house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the photographer##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
10. the engineer is on the right of the musician##1
11. the tower house is the accountant##1
12. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the journalist##1
14. the ranch-style house is the person drinking water##1
15. the craftsman house is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
