 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
